<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=2 -->
FOR FURTHER INFORMATION CONTACT:
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
 Dom Nessi, Director, Office of Native American Programs, Room 4140, 451 Seventh Street, SW., Washington, DC 20410,
telephone (202) 708&hyph;1015. A telecommunications device for speech and/or hearing impaired persons (TDD) is
